<para>This function is called for each step of a particle in the simulation. It checks if the event is a fast simulation event, and if not, it calls the <computeroutput>AnalyzeStandardStep</computeroutput> function to analyze the standard step. If the event is a fast simulation event, it performs various operations based on the particle&apos;s properties and the current volume.</para>
